thread.title: Fred

author: Fred
title: Fred
text: Can't say enough good things. First, the trees were in great condition. Second, the price was good. And finally, the shipping seemed kinda high, but proved worth every penny. The trees were securely bundled and wrapped in bubble wrap and in a sturdy box. Good thing too, cause the Fed Ex guy ignored the "This end up" sticker. Awesome experience all around. Keep up the good work.
